    "text294": "Our history",
    "text295": "With a passion for programming and a deep understanding of its impact, Programming Prodigy was founded in 2019. Since then, we have helped countless students, professionals, and coding enthusiasts embark on successful programming journeys. Our team of experienced instructors brings a wealth of knowledge and industry expertise to guide you through every step of your learning process.",
